Scott interviews Tim Kelly of the Future of Freedom Foundation, author of the recent article, &quot;The MAD Myth,&quot; about the Mutually-Assured-Destruction paradigm. &lt;a href=&quot;
http://www.fff.org/comment/com1208j.asp&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://www.fff.org/comment/com1208j.asp&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;
